{"id":403,"ayahs":[{"number":53,"arabic":"وَيَسْتَعْجِلُونَكَ بِٱلْعَذَابِ ۚ وَلَوْلَآ أَجَلٌۭ مُّسَمًّۭى لَّجَآءَهُمُ ٱلْعَذَابُ وَلَيَأْتِيَنَّهُم بَغْتَةًۭ وَهُمْ لَا يَشْعُرُونَ","translation":"Now they challenge thee to hasten the coming upon them of [God’s] chastisement: and indeed, had not a term been set [for it by God], that suffering would already have come upon them! But indeed, it will most certainly come upon them of a sudden, and they will be taken unawares.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3393.mp3","surahId":29,"words":[{"id":50718,"position":1,"arabic":"وَيَسْتَعْجِلُونَكَ","translation":"আর তোমার (নিকট)দাবী করে এগিয়ে আনতে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_053_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":50719,"position":2,"arabic":"بِٱلْعَذَابِ ۚ","translation":"বিষয়টি শাস্তির","audioUrl":"wbw/029_053_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":50721,"position":3,"arabic":"وَلَوْلَآ","translation":"কিন্তু যদি না (থাকতো)","audioUrl":"wbw/029_053_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":50722,"position":4,"arabic":"أَجَلٌۭ","translation":"সময়","audioUrl":"wbw/029_053_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":50723,"position":5,"arabic":"مُّسَمًّۭى","translation":"নির্ধারিত","audioUrl":"wbw/029_053_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":50724,"position":6,"arabic":"لَّجَآءَهُمُ","translation":"অবশ্যই আসতো তাদের (উপর)","audioUrl":"wbw/029_053_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":50725,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلْعَذَابُ","translation":"শাস্তি","audioUrl":"wbw/029_053_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":50726,"position":8,"arabic":"وَلَيَأْتِيَنَّهُم","translation":"এবং অবশ্যই আসবেই উপর তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/029_053_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":50727,"position":9,"arabic":"بَغْتَةًۭ","translation":"হঠাৎ করে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_053_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":50728,"position":10,"arabic":"وَهُمْ","translation":"এ অবস্থায় যে তারা","audioUrl":"wbw/029_053_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":50729,"position":11,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/029_053_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":50730,"position":12,"arabic":"يَشْعُرُونَ","translation":"টেরও পাবে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_053_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":50731,"position":13,"arabic":"٥٣","translation":"(৫৩)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":54,"arabic":"يَسْتَعْجِلُونَكَ بِٱلْعَذَابِ وَإِنَّ جَهَنَّمَ لَمُحِيطَةٌۢ بِٱلْكَٰفِرِينَ","translation":"They challenge thee to hasten the coming upon them of [God’s] chastisement: but, verily, hell is bound to encompass all who deny the truth –","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3394.mp3","surahId":29,"words":[{"id":51099,"position":1,"arabic":"يَسْتَعْجِلُونَكَ","translation":"তোমার (কাছে) দাবী করে এগিয়ে আনতে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_054_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51100,"position":2,"arabic":"بِٱلْعَذَابِ","translation":"বিষয়টি শাস্তির","audioUrl":"wbw/029_054_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51101,"position":3,"arabic":"وَإِنَّ","translation":"অথচ নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/029_054_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51102,"position":4,"arabic":"جَهَنَّمَ","translation":"জাহান্নাম","audioUrl":"wbw/029_054_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51103,"position":5,"arabic":"لَمُحِيطَةٌۢ","translation":"অবশ্যই পরিবেষ্টনকারী","audioUrl":"wbw/029_054_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51104,"position":6,"arabic":"بِٱلْكَـٰفِرِينَ","translation":"নিয়ে কাফেরদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_054_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51105,"position":7,"arabic":"٥٤","translation":"(৫৪)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":55,"arabic":"يَوْمَ يَغْشَىٰهُمُ ٱلْعَذَابُ مِن فَوْقِهِمْ وَمِن تَحْتِ أَرْجُلِهِمْ وَيَقُولُ ذُوقُوا۟ مَا كُنتُمْ تَعْمَلُونَ","translation":"[encompass them] on the Day when suffering will overwhelm them from above them and from beneath their feet, whereupon He shall say: “Taste [now the fruit of] your own doings!”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3395.mp3","surahId":29,"words":[{"id":51884,"position":1,"arabic":"يَوْمَ","translation":"সেদিন","audioUrl":"wbw/029_055_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51885,"position":2,"arabic":"يَغْشَىٰهُمُ","translation":"ঢেকে ফেলবে তাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_055_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51886,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْعَذَابُ","translation":"শাস্তি","audioUrl":"wbw/029_055_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51887,"position":4,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"হ'তে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_055_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51888,"position":5,"arabic":"فَوْقِهِمْ","translation":"উপর তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/029_055_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51889,"position":6,"arabic":"وَمِن","translation":"ও হ'তে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_055_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51890,"position":7,"arabic":"تَحْتِ","translation":"নিচ","audioUrl":"wbw/029_055_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51891,"position":8,"arabic":"أَرْجُلِهِمْ","translation":"পায়ের তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/029_055_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51892,"position":9,"arabic":"وَيَقُولُ","translation":"আর তিনি বলবেন","audioUrl":"wbw/029_055_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51893,"position":10,"arabic":"ذُوقُوا۟","translation":"\"তোমরা স্বাদ নাও","audioUrl":"wbw/029_055_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51894,"position":11,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"যা কিছু","audioUrl":"wbw/029_055_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51895,"position":12,"arabic":"كُنتُمْ","translation":"তোমরা ছিলে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_055_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51896,"position":13,"arabic":"تَعْمَلُونَ","translation":"তোমরা কাজ করতে\"","audioUrl":"wbw/029_055_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51897,"position":14,"arabic":"٥٥","translation":"(৫৫)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":56,"arabic":"يَٰعِبَادِىَ ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوٓا۟ إِنَّ أَرْضِى وَٰسِعَةٌۭ فَإِيَّٰىَ فَٱعْبُدُونِ","translation":"O YOU servants of Mine who have attained to faith! Behold, wide is Mine earth: worship Me, then, Me alone!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3396.mp3","surahId":29,"words":[{"id":52211,"position":1,"arabic":"يَـٰعِبَادِىَ","translation":"হে আমার দাসরা","audioUrl":"wbw/029_056_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52212,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/029_056_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52213,"position":3,"arabic":"ءَامَنُوٓا۟","translation":"ঈমান এনেছো","audioUrl":"wbw/029_056_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52214,"position":4,"arabic":"إِنَّ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/029_056_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52215,"position":5,"arabic":"أَرْضِى","translation":"আমার পৃথিবী","audioUrl":"wbw/029_056_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52216,"position":6,"arabic":"وَٰسِعَةٌۭ","translation":"প্রশস্ত","audioUrl":"wbw/029_056_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52217,"position":7,"arabic":"فَإِيَّـٰىَ","translation":"সুতরাং শুধু আমারই","audioUrl":"wbw/029_056_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52218,"position":8,"arabic":"فَٱعْبُدُونِ","translation":"অতএব তোমরা ইবাদাত করো আমারই","audioUrl":"wbw/029_056_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52219,"position":9,"arabic":"٥٦","translation":"(৫৬)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":57,"arabic":"كُلُّ نَفْسٍۢ ذَآئِقَةُ ٱلْمَوْتِ ۖ ثُمَّ إِلَيْنَا تُرْجَعُونَ","translation":"Every human being is bound to taste death, [and] in the end unto Us shall all be brought back:","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3397.mp3","surahId":29,"words":[{"id":52953,"position":1,"arabic":"كُلُّ","translation":"প্রত্যেক","audioUrl":"wbw/029_057_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52954,"position":2,"arabic":"نَفْسٍۢ","translation":"প্রাণই","audioUrl":"wbw/029_057_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52955,"position":3,"arabic":"ذَآئِقَةُ","translation":"স্বাদ গ্রহণকারী","audioUrl":"wbw/029_057_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52956,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْمَوْتِ ۖ","translation":"মৃত্যুর","audioUrl":"wbw/029_057_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52958,"position":5,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","translation":"অতঃপর","audioUrl":"wbw/029_057_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52959,"position":6,"arabic":"إِلَيْنَا","translation":"দিকেই আমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/029_057_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52960,"position":7,"arabic":"تُرْجَعُونَ","translation":"তোমরা প্রত্যাবর্তিত হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_057_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52961,"position":8,"arabic":"٥٧","translation":"(৫৭)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":58,"arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوا۟ وَعَمِلُوا۟ ٱلصَّٰلِحَٰتِ لَنُبَوِّئَنَّهُم مِّنَ ٱلْجَنَّةِ غُرَفًۭا تَجْرِى مِن تَحْتِهَا ٱلْأَنْهَٰرُ خَٰلِدِينَ فِيهَا ۚ نِعْمَ أَجْرُ ٱلْعَٰمِلِينَ","translation":"whereupon unto those who have attained to faith and wrought good works We shall most certainly assign mansions in that paradise through which run­ning waters flow, therein to abide: how excellent a reward for those who labour –","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3398.mp3","surahId":29,"words":[{"id":53475,"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"এবং যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/029_058_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53476,"position":2,"arabic":"ءَامَنُوا۟","translation":"ঈমান এনেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_058_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53477,"position":3,"arabic":"وَعَمِلُوا۟","translation":"ও কাজ করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_058_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53478,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلصَّـٰلِحَـٰتِ","translation":"সৎ","audioUrl":"wbw/029_058_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53479,"position":5,"arabic":"لَنُبَوِّئَنَّهُم","translation":"অবশ্যই বসবাস করাবোই তাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_058_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53480,"position":6,"arabic":"مِّنَ","translation":"এর","audioUrl":"wbw/029_058_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53481,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلْجَنَّةِ","translation":"জান্নাতে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_058_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53482,"position":8,"arabic":"غُرَفًۭا","translation":"সুউচ্চ প্রাসাদসমূহে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_058_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53483,"position":9,"arabic":"تَجْرِى","translation":"প্রবাহিত হয়","audioUrl":"wbw/029_058_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53484,"position":10,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"দিয়ে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_058_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53485,"position":11,"arabic":"تَحْتِهَا","translation":"নিচ তার","audioUrl":"wbw/029_058_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53486,"position":12,"arabic":"ٱلْأَنْهَـٰرُ","translation":"ঝর্ণাধারাসমূহ","audioUrl":"wbw/029_058_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53487,"position":13,"arabic":"خَـٰلِدِينَ","translation":"তারা চিরস্থায়ী হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_058_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53488,"position":14,"arabic":"فِيهَا ۚ","translation":"মধ্যে তার","audioUrl":"wbw/029_058_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53490,"position":15,"arabic":"نِعْمَ","translation":"কত উত্তম","audioUrl":"wbw/029_058_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53491,"position":16,"arabic":"أَجْرُ","translation":"প্রতিদান","audioUrl":"wbw/029_058_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53492,"position":17,"arabic":"ٱلْعَـٰمِلِينَ","translation":"কর্মশীলদের (আমলকারীদের)","audioUrl":"wbw/029_058_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53493,"position":18,"arabic":"٥٨","translation":"(৫৮)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":59,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ صَبَرُوا۟ وَعَلَىٰ رَبِّهِمْ يَتَوَكَّلُونَ","translation":"those who are patient in adversity and in their Sustainer place their trust!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3399.mp3","surahId":29,"words":[{"id":53969,"position":1,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/029_059_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53970,"position":2,"arabic":"صَبَرُوا۟","translation":"ধৈর্য ধরেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_059_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53971,"position":3,"arabic":"وَعَلَىٰ","translation":"আর উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/029_059_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53972,"position":4,"arabic":"رَبِّهِمْ","translation":"রবের তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/029_059_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53973,"position":5,"arabic":"يَتَوَكَّلُونَ","translation":"তারা নির্ভর করে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_059_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53974,"position":6,"arabic":"٥٩","translation":"(৫৯)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":60,"arabic":"وَكَأَيِّن مِّن دَآبَّةٍۢ لَّا تَحْمِلُ رِزْقَهَا ٱللَّهُ يَرْزُقُهَا وَإِيَّاكُمْ ۚ وَهُوَ ٱلسَّمِيعُ ٱلْعَلِيمُ","translation":"And how many a living creature is there that takes no thought of its own sustenance; [the while] God provides for it as [He provides] for you - since He alone is all-hearing, all-knowing.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3400.mp3","surahId":29,"words":[{"id":54371,"position":1,"arabic":"وَكَأَيِّن","translation":"এবং এমন অনেক আছে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_060_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":54372,"position":2,"arabic":"مِّن","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_060_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":54373,"position":3,"arabic":"دَآبَّةٍۢ","translation":"জীব-জন্তর","audioUrl":"wbw/029_060_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":54374,"position":4,"arabic":"لَّا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/029_060_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":54375,"position":5,"arabic":"تَحْمِلُ","translation":"বহন করে (মওজুদ রাখে)","audioUrl":"wbw/029_060_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":54376,"position":6,"arabic":"رِزْقَهَا","translation":"জীবিকা তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/029_060_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":54377,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহই","audioUrl":"wbw/029_060_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":54378,"position":8,"arabic":"يَرْزُقُهَا","translation":"জীবিকা দেন তাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_060_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":54379,"position":9,"arabic":"وَإِيَّاكُمْ ۚ","translation":"আর তোমাদেরক